-\fIaffile,afprog,afsocket,afuser,basicfuncs,csvparser,dbparser,syslogformat,afsql\fR\&. Available only in
+\fIaffile, afprog, afsocket, afuser, basicfuncs, csvparser, dbparser, syslogformat, afsql\fR\&. Available only in
 syslog\-ng Open Source Edition 3\&.3
 and later\&.
 .RE
